videos.headline: Peppers' bid for punt return TD falls just short
videos.description: Jabrill Peppers returns a Penn State punt 53 yards before losing his footing while running toward the end zone.

videos.headline: Michigan's 4th-and-goal gamble pays off
videos.description: On 4th-and-goal from the one-yard line, Michigan TE Khalid Hill scores to give the Wolverines a 7-0 lead over Penn State.

videos.headline: Michigan goes up 14 over Penn State
videos.description: De'Veon Smith scores from two yards out to give Michigan a 14-0 lead over Penn State.

videos.headline: Several Michigan players raise fists during national anthem
videos.description: Several Michigan players raise their fists during the national anthem prior to the Wolverines' game against Penn State.

videos.headline: Penn State LB ejected for targeting
videos.description: Penn State LB Brandon Smith is ejected for targeting on this hard hit near the goal line against Michigan.

videos.headline: Speight hits Asiasi for three-yard TD
